  Find a GOOD body/paint shop. Dave with the 1960 DD sunroof standerd kombi
(in Phoenix) did a lot of metal work to the bus and repainted the areas he
fixed. He had paint matched to the OG paint blended in the repaired areas
and you CANNOT tell where he made the repairs. If you are in or near the
Phoenix area I would take it to him for repairs.
http://www.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/66093.jpg  here's a pic of the bus,
you be the judge, it had cut wheel wells, holes for CB atennas and other
misc. fixes.


ronnie

