now require a small bit of body attention.

My problem is I love the original paint and I don't want to paint over it.
Is 
it possible to address the needs of repainting the right side of the bus so 
that it can match? the other 75% of the original paint which is in
remarkably 
good condition.

Can anyone out there guide me in this area. Body shops that may know? 
Unfortunately I live in North Texas so that also constricts So Cal
